<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ قَيْسُ بْنُ يَزِيدَ:</span> <span class="c2">(الخفيف)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ - إِنَّ دَهْراً فِيهِ تَقَنَّعْتَ خَزًّا ... وَتَسَرْبَلْتَ فِي الرِّجَالِ الْبُرُودَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢ - لَزَمَانٌ أَبْدَى النُّحْوسَ إِلَى النَّا ... سِ وَغَطَّى عَنِ الْعُيونِ السُّعُودَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١١٠٨)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ رَبِيعَةُ بْنُ مَقْرُومٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(المديد)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - إِنَّ عَاماً صِرْتَ فِيهِ أَمِيراً ... تَخْبِطُ النَّاسَ لَعَامٌ عُجَابُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - سَادَ عَبَّادٌ وَمُلِّكَ جَيْشاً ... سَبَّحَتْ مِنْ ذَاكَ صُمٌّ صِلابُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١٠٩)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - وَإِنَّ بِقَوْمٍ سَوَّدُوكَ لَفَاقَةً ... إِلَى سَيِّدٍ لَوْ يَظْفَرُونَ بِسَيِّدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١١٠)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ نِعْمَةُ بْنُ عَتَّابٍ التَّغْلِبِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - ألَمْ تَرَ أَنَّ فَحْلَ السَّوْءِ يَسْمُو ... فَيَضْرِبُ خَيْرَةَ الإِبِلِ الصِّعَابِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٢ - سَمَوْتَ وَلَمْ تَكُنْ أَهْلاً لِتَسْمُو ... وَلكِنْ دَهْرُنَا دَهْرُ انْقِلابِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١١١١)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَمْرُو بْنُ مَعدِي كَرِبَ:</span> <span class="c2">(مجزوء الكامل)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>